body:
Hello. I wanted you to guess what some words are in English.
I'll list a word below and you have to guess what it means in English!

Please do not use google translate or other translators.
(Those who have german in school {hopefully not many} can train their vocab)


1.) der Baum
2.) der Lieferheld
3.) Ratgeber
4.) Nachrichten
5.) Boken

New words will follow ._. Harder words and other lenguass. you can post your own words too of course...
I just wanted to see what you'd guess so .-.
